summary: this mod add aquarium to lakeview manor house from hearthfire DLC
descriptionHtml:
adds simple aquarium to Lakeview Manor Home from Hearthfire DLC.
it removes barrels in front the stairs landing (the opposite site of the alchemy lab) so if you stored items there remove them first before using this mod.

Installation : Extract content into your Skyrim/Data folder, or better yet use mod manager
(Nexus mod manager, Mod organizer, etc)

Requires Hearthfire DLC.

Assets from FPI Aquarium kit.

Cleaned with TES5EDIT
author: Lycan888
